### Description

Contrary to https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.componentmodel.design.byteviewer?view=windowsdesktop-9.0&redirectedfrom=MSDN the example below fails to compile with the following error:

> Error	CS0234	The type or namespace name 'ByteViewer' does not exist in the namespace 'System.ComponentModel.Design' (are you missing an assembly reference?)

### Reproduction Steps

```
using System;
using System.Windows.Forms;

namespace MAGNAQuery.View
{
    public partial class formViewer : Form
    {
        public formViewer()
        {
            InitializeComponent();
        }

        void formImageViewer_Load(object sender, EventArgs e)
        {
            var bv = new System.ComponentModel.Design.ByteViewer();
        }
    }
}
```


### Expected behavior

There should be no error.

### Actual behavior

Error	CS0234	The type or namespace name 'ByteViewer' does not exist in the namespace 'System.ComponentModel.Design' (are you missing an assembly reference?)

### Regression?

_No response_

### Known Workarounds

None

### Configuration

.NET 4.8 Winforms project

